Soloing in the planes as a magician is not necessarily easy, but that particular description is very distorted.  Reclaim chaining and aggro kiting are doable, but risky, but neither method is a mana hog.  Pet canni is also a magician's best friend.  KEI is something I regard as a luxury, not a necessity, and has very little impact on my downtime.<br>
